 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#contessa-32-lucy--a-sailing-yacht-with-charm-and-tradition" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Contessa 32&lt;/strong&gt;, designed by David Sadler and built by Jeremy Rogers Ltd, strikes a balance between classic long keel boats and modern fin keel boats. Its semi-long keel with skeg design, inspired by the Contessa 26, offers efficient upwind performance and exceptional seaworthiness. The Contessa 32, renowned for its stability and practical interior layout, is a popular choice for sailors prioritizing comfort and performance at sea.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://lucy.hamburg/boot/featured.jpeg"/></item></channel></rss>